          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: </strong>What are your favorite fashion trends of all time?</p><p><strong>A: </strong>Tracksuits for everyone… and messy hair…together or separate ;) </p><p><strong>Q: </strong>Any upcoming personal projects you’d like to share with us or a sneak peak?</p><p><strong>A: </strong>I just started working on a book of short stories. If you enjoy reading, my substack is essentially a ‘tell-all’ and you can see almost everything I’ve written recently on there…if you see me say hi</p>",
